## Remarks  
<span data-ttu-id="72399-276">メソッド`Close`は、に関連付けられているアン<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>マネージリソースとマネージリソースの両方を解放します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72399-276">The `Close` method frees both unmanaged and managed resources associated with the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="72399-277">が<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>基になる<xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>を所有している場合は、それも閉じられます。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72399-277">If the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> owns the underlying <xref:System.Net.Sockets.Socket>, it is closed as well.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="72399-278">がに関連付けら<xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>れている`Close`場合、メソッドは TCP 接続を終了しますが、関連<xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>付けられているの dispose は破棄しません。 <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72399-278">If a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream> was associated with a <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>, the `Close` method will close the TCP connection, but not dispose of the associated <xref:System.Net.Sockets.TcpClient>.</span></span>

## Examples  
<span data-ttu-id="72399-279">を<xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>閉じるコード例を次に示します。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="72399-279">The following code example closes the <xref:System.Net.Sockets.NetworkStream>.</span></span>

```vb
' Example for closing the NetworkStream.
' Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close()
```

```csharp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.

// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream.Close();
```

```cpp
// Example for closing the NetworkStream.
// Close the NetworkStream
myNetworkStream->Close();
```
